            "answer_text": "Why couldn\u2019t they be? An \u201ceyewitness\u201d is someone who was present and who noticed when something happened. A blind person can\u2019t describe the way things LOOKED, but they certainly can describe the way things sounded, smelled, etc., and descriptive details like these very much can matter to the case at hand. ",
